{"about_the_game":"<i>Requires Open Beta 2.8</i> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/extras/maincol_gradient_rule.png?t=1727190326\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DCS: Black Shark 3</h2></strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/extras/Banner-1.gif?t=1727190326\" /><br><br>A further development of the well-known Black Shark and Black Shark 2 projects, which are dedicated to the Russian Ka-50 attack helicopter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/extras/Banner-3.gif?t=1727190326\" /><br><br>The Ka-50 is the world's only single-seat coaxial combat helicopter. It can effectively perform anti-tank missions, provide close air support and hit point targets on the battlefield with a wide range of weapons.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/extras/Banner-4.gif?t=1727190326\" /><br><br>The Black Shark 3 version implements new functionality such as: Igla air-to-air missiles, which significantly expand the air-to-air capabilities and a new defence system that detects missiles launched at the helicopter. Also, for the first time in DCS, a physical model of the Inertial Navigation System (INS) has been implemented with all features including: alignment before the flight, drift error accumulation and the ability to correct according to preset fixpoints.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/extras/Banner-5.gif?t=1727190326\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Air-to-Air missiles \u201cIgla\u201d<br></li><li>Defensive Missile Warning System<br></li><li>Detailed model of the Inertial Navigation System (INS)<br></li><li>A completely new 3D model created using modern technology<br></li><li>Detailed 3D cockpit with 6 Degrees of Freedom<br></li><li>Professional Flight Model that accurately simulates the characteristics of a coaxial helicopter<br></li><li>Deep study of helicopter systems and equipment: sighting and navigation system, weapons control system, engines, radio equipment, cockpit instruments, fuel, electrical and hydraulic systems.<br></li><li>All standard weapons of the helicopter have been implemented including: ATGM &quot;Vikhr&quot;, rockets, bombs and internal flexible gun</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/extras/maincol_gradient_rule.png?t=1727190326\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Localization:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cockpit: English, Russian<br></li><li>Radio: English, Russian<br></li><li>Manual: English, Russian</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727190326","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/page.bg.jpg?t=1727190326","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727190326","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214600/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727190326","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"VR Support","id":31},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<i>Requires Open Be